{"type": "article", "id": 23381, "title": "折叠雨衣", "description": "", "date": "2016-03-07T07:00:18Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 56, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702133752quo1HMIYkQe3PfcL.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这是荷兰自行车品牌 VANMOOF 专为城市骑行者设计的折叠式雨衣，拉开拉链后就直接弹出一件雨衣，从头覆盖到手，弧度可以引导雨水滑落。它的圆框结构刚好在手的位置，有一定的固定作用，可以防止滑落。将它缩小成圆形的小包后能直接挂在自行车车杆下，很方便。可以选择蓝、灰、黄三种颜色和三种型号，<a href=\"http://vanmoof.com/boncho/156-boncho-mint.html\">这里是预定链接。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021337506sbepiUq2Kf5MLy1.gif\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.64095238\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133750mcUC5dk4SG0Po9DM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.25047619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133751KU9jJ6AHie8DB5Nc.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133751QqHhocGa4vfdsl9D.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.49117647\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n\n\n"}